{"tid":207632,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"其實搵工又有乜好怕喎....","createTime":"2017-04-19T04:06:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-19T05:27:00.000Z","uid":83183,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"673593c046e37d126b31aa63b53fa15a9086f077","tid":207632,"uid":83183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T04:06:11.000Z","msg":"有無試過畢業之後好唔想搵工，搵左又唔想返工...<br />\n有無試過坐係公司，望住個堆要做既野，都唔點解會關自己事...<br />\n<br />\n我曾經都係一個朝9晚5，每星期一朝早 on99 咁好唔想返工....<br />\n直到上年我把心一橫同個朋友出黎創業，搞搞下又好似幾好.... <br />\n未死得之餘仲可以請多d人...<br />\n<br />\n其實我都好想係香港創造一個好好既工作環境，同事可以選擇自己想做d乜，可以選擇公司大家一齊想做d乜，大家一齊返工好似一齊去玩咁<br />\n<br />\n有無廢青有相同既感覺？"},{"pid":"ec2d6dec470b07afd5531aea8968b1dcbe0799bc","tid":207632,"uid":14965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T04:08:52.000Z","msg":"那有錢"},{"pid":"2359751815eddf7cfb3dc0d34fd90788faf414c8","tid":207632,"uid":83183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T04:11:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>那有錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪真絲？有無力？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有力請埋你一齊玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e8604865d778a6d77018ad569836136b92409a4","tid":207632,"uid":60065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T04:16:49.000Z","msg":"請唔請人呀巴打"},{"pid":"1401db15bb39b2ef4a375e40e1f3e40705045884","tid":207632,"uid":21530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T04:19:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>那有錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪真絲？有無力？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有力請埋你一齊玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n請埋我"},{"pid":"b25b0648cdbe04aad920711786c0ed27d6577b9e","tid":207632,"uid":242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T04:25:50.000Z","msg":"做D乜？<br />\n有咩要求？<br />\n人工幾多？<br />\n工時係點？"},{"pid":"2a696c386e3d96ffabc647ec4fba9fcea84f178a